# === NAS IT Smart Solutions Project Rules ===
# Purpose: High-quality business website for refurbished IT device reseller
# Framework: Next.js (App Router) + Tailwind + shadcn + Typescript

- Use clean and professional UI.
- Prioritize credibility (trust elements, director experience).
- Put **WhatsApp CTA** on every page.
- Focus on responsive layout – mobile first.
- Use metadata and structured SEO tags.
- Keep code organized with `/components/` folder.
- Use `lib/seo.ts` for metadata.
- Always create with production deployment in mind.

# Pages to Create:
- app/page.tsx (Home)
- app/about/page.tsx
- app/services/page.tsx
- app/projects/page.tsx
- app/contact/page.tsx
- app/api/contact/route.ts (Form handler)

# Libraries:
- shadcn/ui
- TailwindCSS
- Next SEO (optional)
- React Hook Form (for contact form)

# Writing Style:
- Tone: Professional, reliable, experienced.
- Avoid jargon.
- Emphasize affordability + quality assurance.

# Future proofing:
- Prepare for e-commerce (but don’t build yet).
- Use reusable components.
